---
---

<section id="experiencia" class="tandem-experience">
  <div class="experience-container container">
    <div class="experience-grid">
      <div class="experience-content">
        <span class="experience-tag">Experiencia Transformadora</span>
        <h2 class="experience-title">
          No es solo un salto.<br />
          <span class="experience-accent">Es una experiencia transformadora</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="experience-description">
          Desde las alturas, contempla la espectacular belleza del desierto y la bahía de Paracas como nunca antes la habías visto. Cada segundo en el aire combina adrenalina, libertad y una sensación indescriptible que permanecerá contigo para siempre.
        </p>
        <div class="experience-features">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Vistas del desierto y bahía de Paracas</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
            </svg>
            <span>60 segundos de caída libre a 140 mph</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Video HD de obsequio incluido</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="experience-buttons">
          <a href="https://skipperu.odoo.com/tandem-oro" class="btn-platinum" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Ver Plan Platinum
          </a>
          <a href="https://skipperu.odoo.com/shop/tdms-salto-tandem-safiro-3" class="btn-reservar-experience" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Reservar
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="experience-image-wrapper">
        <img src="/images/FOTO_FINTA.webp" alt="Vista aérea del desierto y bahía de Paracas" class="experience-image" />
        <div class="experience-image-badge">
          <span class="badge-number">9,000</span>
          <span class="badge-text">Pies de altura</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .tandem-experience {
    background-color: var(--bg-celeste);
    padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
  }

  .experience-container {
    max-width: var(--container-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--container-padding-x);
  }

  .experience-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .experience-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--primary-blue);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 40px;
  }

  .experience-tag::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    width: 28px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: var(--primary-blue);
  }

  .experience-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .experience-accent {
    color: var(--primary-blue);
  }

  .experience-description {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-text);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .experience-features {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .feature-item svg {
    color: var(--primary-blue);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .experience-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .btn-platinum {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    background-color: var(--accent-gold);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-family: var(--font-header);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    transition: var(--transition);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-platinum:hover {
    background-color: #e6bc00;
  }

  .btn-reservar-experience {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    background-color: var(--primary-blue);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-header);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    transition: var(--transition);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-reservar-experience:hover {
    background-color: var(--primary-dark);
  }

  .experience-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
  }

  .experience-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 560px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .experience-image-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 32px;
    left: 32px;
    background-color: var(--bg-dark);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    padding: 20px 28px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .badge-number {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 42px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--primary-blue);
  }

  .badge-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 80px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .experience-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }

    .experience-image {
      height: 400px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .tandem-experience {
      padding: 48px 0;
    }

    .experience-image {
      height: 320px;
    }

    .experience-image-badge {
      bottom: 20px;
      left: 20px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
    }

    .badge-number {
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .experience-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .btn-platinum,
    .btn-reservar-experience {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
